works.description:
We are Taxi, Car Rental & Bus services  
provider based in Penang Island, Malaysia. We have "red" budget taxi; and 

executive/luxury "blue" taxi, like Toyota Avanza, Naza Ria 2.5(A), Naza  
Citra 2.0, Nissan Sylphy 2.0, Toyota Innova; and budget "red" taxi like  
Proton Saga, Proton Wira, Proton Waja and Nissan Sentra. Other luxury cars
 
we have for hire are Toyota Camry, Nissan Teana 2011, BMW, and Toyota Wish
 
2011.


Indranx Transport Services business includes Taxi fleet management and  
operations, 24 hours Radio call centre & Outdoor Mobile taxi advertising. 

We cater for both taxi market segment, premier and budget taxi services.  

All of our taxis are less than five years old and are fuelled by either  
Natural Gas Vehicle (NGV) or Unleaded Petrol as part of our environment  
care initiative. We operate at Penang Island and also Seberang jaya with
77  
taxis. The call centre operates 24 hours per day and over 365 days in a  
year and they provide a comprehensive 3 channels communication in English,
 
Bahasa Malaysia and Mandarin languages for the customers








Our Services:


* Point to point transfer


* One way transfer


* Return Transfer


* Airport Transfer (Penang International Airport)


* Jetty or Railway station transfer (Butterworth, Penang)


* Bus terminal transfer


* Leisure Travelling


* Business Travelling


* Corporate Events


* Charter service


* City Tours


* Family Vacation

* VIP Chauffer Driven


* Overland Tour
